name: Fuku-Kun
description: The $FUKU project was launched to celebrate the friendship between KabosuMama, the owner of the famous Doge meme Shiba Inu, and a cute puppy discovered on her walks, Fuku-kun. The token embodies the values of friendship, happiness, and collaboration, drawing inspiration from Fuku-kun's joyful spirit and the bond he shares with KabosuMama. The project features a meme token with no taxes, no team-controlled tokens, and a fully renounced smart contract.
